1
00:01:28,534 --> 00:01:32,401
- INUYASHA!

2
00:01:35,468 --> 00:01:37,268
- HA HA!

3
00:01:44,001 --> 00:01:46,001
HUH.

4
00:02:00,968 --> 00:02:02,101
HMM! SO THERE.

5
00:02:02,134 --> 00:02:06,334
FINALLY, THE WAY FOR ME
TO BECOME ALL DEMON AT LAST.

6
00:02:06,368 --> 00:02:08,001
HUH!

7
00:02:10,101 --> 00:02:12,668
- INUYASHA!

8
00:02:36,601 --> 00:02:39,701
K-KIKYO?

9
00:02:39,734 --> 00:02:43,301
HOW COULD--
I THOUGHT--

10
00:02:47,201 --> 00:02:50,834
- [GRUNTING]

11
00:02:52,968 --> 00:02:56,134
- BIG SISTER!
- LADY KIKYO!
THAT WOUND, IT--

12
00:02:56,168 --> 00:02:58,634
- YOU'RE HURT REALLY BADLY.

13
00:02:58,668 --> 00:03:03,201
- I FORGOT WHO I--
AND NOW SEE WHAT--

14
00:03:03,234 --> 00:03:04,068
UH...

15
00:03:04,101 --> 00:03:08,068
ALL FOR THIS,
THE SACRED JEWEL WHICH--

16
00:03:08,101 --> 00:03:08,801
UH!

17
00:03:08,834 --> 00:03:12,034
- YOU'RE IN PAIN.
LET SOMEONE--

18
00:03:12,068 --> 00:03:14,534
- I WON'T FEEL IT MUCH LONGER,

19
00:03:14,568 --> 00:03:17,434
AND SO I GIVE THIS TO YOU--

20
00:03:17,468 --> 00:03:19,201
THE SHIKON NO TAMA,

21
00:03:19,234 --> 00:03:22,034
WHICH YOU MUST BURN
WITH MY BODY.

22
00:03:22,068 --> 00:03:28,301
IT MUST NOT FALL INTO THE HANDS
OF THOSE WHO WOULD ABUSE IT.

23
00:03:29,868 --> 00:03:31,401
UNG...UH.

24
00:03:31,434 --> 00:03:33,234
- SISTER KIKYO.

25
00:03:33,268 --> 00:03:36,368
SISTER KIKYO!

26
00:03:36,401 --> 00:03:41,368
- I SHALL TAKE IT WITH ME
TO THE OTHER WORLD.

27
00:04:00,001 --> 00:04:01,568
- SHIKON NO WHAT?

28
00:04:01,601 --> 00:04:04,368
- SHIKON NO TAMA, MY GIRL--

29
00:04:04,401 --> 00:04:06,701
THE JEWEL OF 4 SOULS.

30
00:04:06,734 --> 00:04:12,068
- YOU DON'T ACTUALLY THINK
TOURISTS ARE GONNA BUY THESE
DUMB KEY CHAINS, DO YOU?

31
00:04:12,101 --> 00:04:14,834
- THAT IS NOT JUST A KEY CHAIN.

32
00:04:14,868 --> 00:04:16,501
THAT CRYSTAL THERE AT THE END

33
00:04:16,534 --> 00:04:20,668
IS A REPLICA OF
AN ANCIENT JEWEL WHICH--

34
00:04:20,701 --> 00:04:22,801
HMM?

35
00:04:25,134 --> 00:04:26,834
- HMM?

36
00:04:27,968 --> 00:04:29,934
- AHEM. AS I WAS SAYING,

37
00:04:29,968 --> 00:04:35,301
THAT CRYSTAL IS A REPLICA
OF AN ANCIENT JEWEL WHICH--

38
00:04:36,234 --> 00:04:37,701
MMPH!

39
00:04:37,734 --> 00:04:38,834
AN ANCIENT JEWEL--

40
00:04:38,868 --> 00:04:43,168
- YOU DO REMEMBER IT'S
MY BIRTHDAY TOMORROW, RIGHT?

41
00:04:43,201 --> 00:04:44,134
- HA HA HA!

42
00:04:44,168 --> 00:04:46,468
I'D PLANNED TO WAIT
ANOTHER DAY, BUT--

43
00:04:46,501 --> 00:04:48,801
- SO YOU DID GET SOMETHING.
HAND IT OVER.

44
00:04:48,834 --> 00:04:54,801
- THAT, MY DEAR, IS
AN AUTHENTIC MUMMIFIED HAND
OF A WATER IMP, WHICH--

45
00:04:54,834 --> 00:04:57,868
- HERE, BUYO. EAT.

46
00:04:57,901 --> 00:05:00,834
- WAAH! THAT'S AN ANTIQUE!

47
00:05:00,868 --> 00:05:02,734
[MUTTERS]

48
00:05:02,768 --> 00:05:05,534
- REPLICA THIS,
AUTHENTIC THAT.

49
00:05:05,568 --> 00:05:07,568
HERE, EVERYTHING
HAS GOT A STORY.

50
00:05:07,601 --> 00:05:10,701
- WHY, THESE PICKLES
ARE FULL OF HISTORY.

51
00:05:10,734 --> 00:05:13,568
- NOT HALF AS FULL AS YOU ARE.

52
00:05:13,601 --> 00:05:14,701
- MM!

53
00:05:14,734 --> 00:05:17,868
- THE THOUSAND-YEAR-OLD
SACRED TREE,

54
00:05:17,901 --> 00:05:20,601
THE LEGEND
OF THE HIDDEN WELL--

55
00:05:20,634 --> 00:05:23,301
I'VE HEARD THESE STORIES
ALL MY LIFE,

56
00:05:23,334 --> 00:05:26,534
AND I'VE NEVER BELIEVED
A WORD OF IT...

57
00:05:26,568 --> 00:05:32,801
THAT IS, TILL TODAY,
MY 15th BIRTHDAY.

58
00:05:44,501 --> 00:05:46,868
I'M LEAVING.

59
00:05:49,801 --> 00:05:52,501
HEY, WHAT ARE YOU--

60
00:05:52,534 --> 00:05:53,468
- NOTHING.

61
00:05:53,501 --> 00:05:56,334
- YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED
TO PLAY IN THERE.

62
00:05:56,368 --> 00:05:58,268
- I'M NOT. IT'S THE CAT.

63
00:05:58,301 --> 00:06:02,268
- DID HE GO DOWN TO THE WELL?

64
00:06:02,301 --> 00:06:04,568
- BUYO!

65
00:06:04,601 --> 00:06:08,001
I DON'T KNOW WHERE ELSE
HE CAN BE.

66
00:06:08,034 --> 00:06:08,868
- SO GO DOWN.

67
00:06:08,901 --> 00:06:11,034
- BUT WHY DO I
GOT TO BE THE ONE?

68
00:06:11,068 --> 00:06:14,601
- BECAUSE YOU'RE THE ONE
THAT'S LOOKING FOR HIM.

69
00:06:14,634 --> 00:06:18,068
[SCRATCHING]

70
00:06:18,101 --> 00:06:20,868
- AAH!
SOMETHING IS DOWN THERE!

71
00:06:20,901 --> 00:06:24,268
- UH, YEAH. THE CAT.

72
00:06:27,601 --> 00:06:31,568
THAT SOUND
FROM INSIDE THE WELL--

73
00:06:31,601 --> 00:06:32,501
[THUD]

74
00:06:32,534 --> 00:06:33,468
HMM? AAH!

75
00:06:33,501 --> 00:06:35,934
- AAH! BUYO.

76
00:06:35,968 --> 00:06:38,468
- [PURRS]

77
00:06:39,868 --> 00:06:42,068
- YOU MAKE FUN OF ME
BECAUSE I'M SCARED,

78
00:06:42,101 --> 00:06:43,768
AND THEN YOU'RE ALL, "AAH!"

79
00:06:43,801 --> 00:06:48,501
- LOOK WHO'S TALKING,
MR. "WHY DO I HAVE TO GO?"

80
00:06:48,534 --> 00:06:49,634
[SCRATCHING]

81
00:06:49,668 --> 00:06:51,234
- UH...UH...

82
00:06:53,301 --> 00:06:55,668
SIS, BEHIND YOU!

83
00:07:01,834 --> 00:07:04,034
- [GASP]

84
00:07:05,901 --> 00:07:08,868
- WHAT'S GOING ON?

85
00:07:19,384 --> 00:07:22,951
- ALIVE.
OH, TO BE ALIVE ONCE MORE.

86
00:07:22,984 --> 00:07:26,717
ALREADY MY STRENGTH RETURNS.

87
00:07:29,917 --> 00:07:32,951
YOU HAVE IT, DON'T YOU?

88
00:07:32,984 --> 00:07:34,384
GIVE IT TO ME.

89
00:07:34,417 --> 00:07:38,517
- WH-WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
LET GO!

90
00:07:42,917 --> 00:07:44,284
- WRETCHED GIRL,

91
00:07:44,317 --> 00:07:47,984
I MUST HAVE THE SACRED JEWEL.

92
00:07:54,951 --> 00:07:58,017
"THE SACRED JEWEL"?

93
00:08:08,617 --> 00:08:13,384
I GUESS I MUST'VE FALLEN
IN THE WELL.

94
00:08:13,417 --> 00:08:17,084
MAYBE I BUMPED
MY HEAD, OR...

95
00:08:17,117 --> 00:08:19,151
UH, MAYBE NOT.

96
00:08:19,184 --> 00:08:21,351
EITHER WAY...

97
00:08:21,384 --> 00:08:25,451
HEY, SOTA?
GET GRANDPA.

98
00:08:25,484 --> 00:08:29,784
HE PROBABLY TOOK OFF, LITTLE--

99
00:08:37,984 --> 00:08:40,251
[STRAINING]

100
00:08:41,951 --> 00:08:43,817
WHAT THE--

101
00:08:46,984 --> 00:08:49,484
I COULD BE WRONG, BUT, TOTO,

102
00:08:49,517 --> 00:08:53,084
I THINK WE'RE NOT
IN TOKYO ANYMORE.

103
00:08:53,117 --> 00:08:57,984
GRANDPA? MOM?
ARE YOU THERE?

104
00:08:59,917 --> 00:09:02,084
SOTA!

105
00:09:02,117 --> 00:09:04,351
BUYO!

106
00:09:06,417 --> 00:09:09,951
IT'S LIKE THE FAMILY SHRINE
IS NOT EVEN--

107
00:09:09,984 --> 00:09:14,084
OH! THE TREE.

108
00:09:17,584 --> 00:09:21,217
THAT MEANS I'M PRACTICALLY HOME.

109
00:09:22,717 --> 00:09:24,417
HUH?

110
00:09:26,817 --> 00:09:30,451
IS THAT A...BOY?

111
00:09:37,684 --> 00:09:42,251
HEY THERE. WHATCHA DOING?

112
00:09:42,884 --> 00:09:47,484
OH, WOW. LIKE DOG EARS.

113
00:09:47,517 --> 00:09:50,851
I THINK I WANT TO TOUCH THEM.

114
00:10:00,417 --> 00:10:03,284
NOW THAT THAT'S
OUT OF MY SYSTEM...

115
00:10:03,317 --> 00:10:06,317
- GET AWAY FROM THERE!

116
00:10:06,351 --> 00:10:08,684
- AAH!

117
00:10:08,717 --> 00:10:10,484
HUH?

118
00:10:12,251 --> 00:10:14,751
UH...

119
00:10:15,451 --> 00:10:19,484
YOU DIDN'T HAVE
TO TIE ME UP, YOU KNOW.

120
00:10:19,517 --> 00:10:21,351
- A GIRL WITH STRANGE CLOTHES.

121
00:10:21,384 --> 00:10:23,351
- IS SHE A FOREIGNER?

122
00:10:23,384 --> 00:10:24,751
- YOU RECKON IT'S A WAR?

123
00:10:24,784 --> 00:10:28,951
- OF COURSE IT IS,
AND RIGHT IN THE MIDDLE OF
RICE-PLANTING SEASON, TOO.

124
00:10:28,984 --> 00:10:31,184
- SHE COULD BE A KITSUNE
IN DISGUISE.

125
00:10:31,217 --> 00:10:35,551
- NAH. THEM SHAPE-CHANGING FOXES
ARE A LOT TRICKIER THAN THAT.

126
00:10:35,584 --> 00:10:37,317
- I'M NOT REALLY SURE OF THAT.

127
00:10:37,351 --> 00:10:40,151
- TOP KNOT.
TOP KNOT, TOP KNOT, TOP KNOT.

128
00:10:40,184 --> 00:10:43,051
WHAT IS THIS, THE JAPAN
OF MEDIEVAL TIMES?

129
00:10:43,084 --> 00:10:46,251
- MAKE WAY
FOR HIGH PRIESTESS KAEDE!

130
00:10:48,917 --> 00:10:50,451
- [SIGH]

131
00:10:50,484 --> 00:10:53,251
NOW WHAT?

132
00:10:55,484 --> 00:10:56,451
- UH!
- UH!

133
00:10:56,484 --> 00:10:57,484
- UH!
- OW!

134
00:10:57,517 --> 00:11:00,817
- DEMON, BE GONE.
- HEY! HEY! I'M NOT A DEMON, OK?

135
00:11:00,851 --> 00:11:01,817
- ARE YE NOT?

136
00:11:01,851 --> 00:11:05,784
THEN WHY WERE YE FOUND
IN THE FOREST OF INUYASHA?

137
00:11:05,817 --> 00:11:08,317
- SHE COULD BE A SPY
FROM ANOTHER VILLAGE.

138
00:11:08,351 --> 00:11:10,851
- IN THAT CASE,
SHE WOULD BE A FOOL.

139
00:11:10,884 --> 00:11:16,551
WHO WOULD INVADE
SUCH A POOR VILLAGE AS OURS?

140
00:11:19,617 --> 00:11:21,717
- HUH?

141
00:11:21,751 --> 00:11:25,017
- LET ME HAVE A GOOD LOOK AT YE.

142
00:11:25,551 --> 00:11:29,851
YOU'RE A CLEVER GIRL?
OR BE YE A HALF-WIT?

143
00:11:29,884 --> 00:11:32,417
- WHY, YOU...

144
00:11:33,184 --> 00:11:37,351
- IT'S THERE,
THOUGH I KNOW NOT WHY.

145
00:11:37,384 --> 00:11:38,851
- HUH?

146
00:11:44,617 --> 00:11:45,751
- STEW?

147
00:11:45,784 --> 00:11:49,284
- WOW. THAT LOOKS GREAT.

148
00:11:49,317 --> 00:11:51,951
REAL FOOD.

149
00:11:52,351 --> 00:11:54,651
- BEAR US NO ILL WILL, CHILD,

150
00:11:54,684 --> 00:11:57,817
FOR THOUGH I NOW SEE
YE MEAN US NO HARM,

151
00:11:57,851 --> 00:11:59,284
IN THESE TROUBLED TIMES OF WAR,

152
00:11:59,317 --> 00:12:04,751
NO STRANGER MAY BE WELCOMED
AMONG US WITHOUT DEEP DISTRUST.

153
00:12:04,784 --> 00:12:08,451
- WE REALLY AREN'T IN TOKYO
ANYMORE, ARE WE?

154
00:12:08,484 --> 00:12:10,851
- TO-KY-O? NEVER HEARD OF IT.

155
00:12:10,884 --> 00:12:12,817
IS THAT WHERE
YOUR PEOPLE ARE FROM?

156
00:12:12,851 --> 00:12:17,384
- UH, YEAH.
SO I, UH, SHOULD GET GOING...

157
00:12:17,417 --> 00:12:22,484
THOUGH I'VE NO IDEA HOW
TO GET BACK, OF COURSE.

158
00:12:25,217 --> 00:12:28,784
- SISTER, PLEASE, YOU MUST.

159
00:12:28,817 --> 00:12:30,617
- TAKE THE JEWEL, KAEDE,

160
00:12:30,651 --> 00:12:35,051
AND SEE THAT IT IS BURNED
WITH MY BODY.

161
00:12:35,684 --> 00:12:41,051
- 50 YEARS
HAVE PASSED SINCE THEN.

162
00:12:50,684 --> 00:12:51,651
[BELL TOLLING]

163
00:12:51,684 --> 00:12:54,651
WHAT'S GOING ON?

164
00:12:54,684 --> 00:12:55,884
OH.
- OH!

165
00:12:55,917 --> 00:13:00,651
- IT'S A MONSTER!
AAH! AAH!

166
00:13:02,784 --> 00:13:05,484
- AAH!
- AAH!
- AAH!

167
00:13:05,517 --> 00:13:07,951
- HA HA!

168
00:13:10,251 --> 00:13:12,484
- IT'S THAT THING.

169
00:13:13,651 --> 00:13:17,451
- GIVE ME THE SACRED JEWEL.

170
00:13:25,151 --> 00:13:27,951
- IT SAID SACRED JEWEL.

171
00:13:27,984 --> 00:13:29,817
ARE YE ITS TILL?

172
00:13:29,851 --> 00:13:31,517
- UH, I HAVE NO IDEA.

173
00:13:31,551 --> 00:13:33,617
I MEAN, I'VE HEARD
OF THE JEWEL, BUT I--

174
00:13:33,651 --> 00:13:38,151
- I MUST HAVE IT. I MUST!

175
00:13:40,217 --> 00:13:43,684
- THAT THING--IT'S AFTER ME.

176
00:13:43,717 --> 00:13:46,151
- SPEARS, ARROWS--
NOTHING WORKS.

177
00:13:46,184 --> 00:13:48,917
- WE MUST LURE IT
TO THE DRY WELL.

178
00:13:48,951 --> 00:13:50,384
- THE DRY WELL?

179
00:13:50,417 --> 00:13:52,517
- IN THE FOREST OF INUYASHA.

180
00:13:52,551 --> 00:13:53,984
- THE WELL I CLIMBED OUT OF.

181
00:13:54,017 --> 00:13:55,517
WHICH WAY IS THE FOREST?

182
00:13:55,551 --> 00:13:57,917
WHERE THE LIGHT
IS SHINING, RIGHT?

183
00:13:57,951 --> 00:14:00,484
- WAIT.

184
00:14:02,051 --> 00:14:03,284
- I'LL DRAW IT AWAY!

185
00:14:03,317 --> 00:14:06,517
HOW IS IT SHE CAN SEE
BUT CANNOT BE SEEN

186
00:14:06,551 --> 00:14:08,884
IN THE FOREST OF INUYASHA?

187
00:14:08,917 --> 00:14:11,251
- LADY KAEDE!

188
00:14:14,284 --> 00:14:17,717
- SOMEONE WILL SAVE ME, RIGHT?

189
00:14:17,751 --> 00:14:19,784
THEY'VE GOT TO.

190
00:14:19,817 --> 00:14:23,984
GRANDPA? MOM? ANYBODY?

191
00:14:24,317 --> 00:14:28,017
WHOEVER YOU ARE,
PLEASE, SOMEBODY, HELP ME!

192
00:14:28,051 --> 00:14:31,717
[MONSTER ROARING]

193
00:14:40,884 --> 00:14:42,551
- I SMELL IT--

194
00:14:42,584 --> 00:14:45,951
THE BLOOD OF THE WOMAN
WHO KILLED ME,

195
00:14:45,984 --> 00:14:48,284
AND IT'S COMING CLOSER.

196
00:14:48,317 --> 00:14:50,817
UGH!

197
00:15:01,632 --> 00:15:04,366
- THE JEWEL--GIVE IT TO ME!

198
00:15:04,399 --> 00:15:08,066
- I TOLD YOU, I DON'T HAVE IT!

199
00:15:10,666 --> 00:15:13,032
UH! AAH! AAAH!

200
00:15:13,066 --> 00:15:15,332
AAAAAH!

201
00:15:15,366 --> 00:15:16,499
OH!

202
00:15:16,532 --> 00:15:22,266
- HELLO, KIKYO.
PLAYING WITH BUGS NOW, ARE WE?

203
00:15:22,299 --> 00:15:23,466
- HUH?

204
00:15:23,499 --> 00:15:26,199
DID HE JUST TALK?

205
00:15:26,232 --> 00:15:27,966
SO YOU'RE ALIVE?

206
00:15:27,999 --> 00:15:30,566
- WHY YOU TAKING
SO LONG TO KILL IT?

207
00:15:30,599 --> 00:15:33,966
JUST DO HER LIKE YOU DID ME.

208
00:15:33,999 --> 00:15:36,732
YOU LOOK PRETTY DUMB
THERE, KIKYO.

209
00:15:36,766 --> 00:15:40,299
THE KIKYO I KNOW
WOULDN'T WASTE HER TIME.

210
00:15:40,332 --> 00:15:41,399
- THAT DOES IT.

211
00:15:41,432 --> 00:15:45,299
KIKYO, KIKYO, WHOEVER SHE IS,
SHE'S NOT ME

212
00:15:45,332 --> 00:15:47,332
BECAUSE MY NAME IS--

213
00:15:47,366 --> 00:15:48,432
- SHE'S HERE.

214
00:15:48,466 --> 00:15:50,599
[MONSTER ROARS]

215
00:15:56,732 --> 00:15:58,332
- GOOD. NOW PULL!

216
00:15:58,366 --> 00:16:00,399
[MEN STRAINING]

217
00:16:00,432 --> 00:16:02,066
- SO I WAS SAVED.

218
00:16:02,099 --> 00:16:04,066
- YOU'RE PATHETIC, KIKYO.

219
00:16:04,099 --> 00:16:06,366
- I'M NOT KIKYO!

220
00:16:06,399 --> 00:16:10,266
LOOK. I'M TELLING YOU,
I'M NOT HER,

221
00:16:10,299 --> 00:16:11,366
WHOEVER HER IS.

222
00:16:11,399 --> 00:16:12,666
- AND I'M SAYING
YOU GOT TO BE HER

223
00:16:12,699 --> 00:16:18,032
BECAUSE IF YOU'RE NOT,
THERE'S NO WAY THAT YOU
COULD SMELL SO--

224
00:16:19,566 --> 00:16:22,166
YOU'RE NOT HER.

225
00:16:22,899 --> 00:16:25,932
- I KNOW. MY NAME IS KAGOME.

226
00:16:25,966 --> 00:16:27,732
KA-GO-ME.

227
00:16:27,766 --> 00:16:32,432
- YOU'RE RIGHT.
KIKYO WAS CUTER, MUCH CUTER.

228
00:16:32,466 --> 00:16:34,799
- WHAT'D YOU--

229
00:16:34,832 --> 00:16:36,732
AAH!

230
00:16:36,766 --> 00:16:38,032
LET GO OF ME!

231
00:16:38,066 --> 00:16:40,966
- OW, OW, OW! YOU LET GO!

232
00:16:40,999 --> 00:16:43,332
- INUYASHA HAS REVIVED.

233
00:16:43,366 --> 00:16:44,766
- HOW CAN THAT BE?

234
00:16:44,799 --> 00:16:48,099
THE SEAL
SHOULD HAVE HELD FOREVER.

235
00:16:48,132 --> 00:16:51,532
- GIVE ME THE SACRED JEWEL!

236
00:16:51,566 --> 00:16:54,766
- SACRED JEWEL?

237
00:16:56,632 --> 00:16:59,566
- STOP IT!

238
00:17:04,999 --> 00:17:06,032
HEY.

239
00:17:06,066 --> 00:17:10,199
I DID THAT BEFORE, TOO,
IN THE WELL...

240
00:17:10,899 --> 00:17:14,999
BUT HOW'D I DO IT, THOUGH?

241
00:17:15,032 --> 00:17:15,766
[GASP]

242
00:17:15,799 --> 00:17:18,099
WHAT'S HAPPENING NOW?

243
00:17:25,566 --> 00:17:27,832
IT CAME FROM INSIDE ME.

244
00:17:27,866 --> 00:17:31,899
IS THAT THE SACRED JEWEL?

245
